appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New features

Enhancements
- Checkin/ Checkout logs data filters by date
- Video preview rotation is now matched with device rotation
- File (PDF) preview rotation is now matched with device rotation
- Portal: Favourite portal, description for each portal, search portal
- Discover enhancements
